It can be ruled out that the police captain of the XXII. district, who killed pedestrians on Tuesday and who has since resigned from his position, was driving under the influence of alcohol or narcotics, the spokesperson of the High Public Prosecutor's Office of the capital city Attila Morvai reported on Friday after the expert opinion of the case was completed.
