Six hundred thousand drivers missed the deadline and did not manage to change their old driver’s license, which expires at the end of the year.
Today is the last day people can apply for an exchange so that the authorities can issue a new card by the end of the year.
However, the Ministry is not afraid that after the New Year hundreds of thousands of drivers without a valid license will go on the road.
