About coffee, rum, cigars, the Sierra Maestra mountains, the Bay of Pigs and the island of Isla de Pinos, about the Tropicana cabaret, about the shrine of Cuban patron Caridad del Cobre, about santeria, about the African religions professed by the descendants of former slaves, about all this one could describe many pages.
